cu.explanation_en: Setting Active_gNBs to an invalid gNB name 'invalid_name' will cause gNB activation and initialization failures during startup.

du.explanation_en: Setting Active_gNBs to an invalid gNB name 'invalid_name' will cause gNB activation and initialization failures during startup.
du.explanation_zh: 將 Active_gNBs 設定為無效的 gNB 名稱 'invalid_name' 會在啟動期間導致 gNB 激活和初始化失敗。
